Detailed Description

Packet for searching out locations from a string naming a location.

\ After the normal header the packet contains: {tabular}{lll} Pos & Size & Destription \ REQUEST_HEADER_SIZE & 4 bytes & locationType \ +4 & 4 bytes & requestedLanguage \ +8 & 4 bytes & nbrLocations \ +12 & 4 bytes & mapID \ +16 & 4 bytes & regionsInMatches \ +20 & 1 byte & uniqueOrFull \ +21 & 1 byte & matching \ +22 & 1 byte & stringpart \ +23 & 1 byte & dbMask \ +24 & 1 byte & minNbrHits \ for nbrLocations & string & location(s) \ {tabular}
